OL,6,FA cleaner from Gloucestershire has
OL,7,Fbeen sentenced after stealing family
OL,8,Fheirlooms worth more than #20,000 from
OL,9,Fher employer.
OL,11,FStephanie Holland, 41, took gold
OL,12,Fwatches and jewellery belonging to
OL,13,FPatricia Clark, 73, from her home
OL,14,Fwhile working for her.
OL,16,FGloucester Crown Court heard Holland
OL,17,Fhow was so trusted by the family that
OL,18,Fshe had a key to their home in
OL,19,FStonehouse.
