OL,6,FShe added: "She said her son had a new
OL,7,Fjob and was treating her. There was
OL,8,Falso a holiday abroad, which was
OL,9,Fcompletely out of character.
OL,11,F"It feels like the ultimate betrayal
OL,12,Fand like a bereavement. I am mourning
OL,13,Fthe loss of sentimental heirlooms.
OL,15,F"It has completely destroyed my trust
OL,16,Fin people, and I am not sure I will
OL,17,Fever get over this."
